---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Privacy Policy" description="Blackout Pickleball privacy policy — how we handle your data.">

  <section class="py-16 sm:py-24 bg-surface">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 prose prose-lg">
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-black tracking-tight mb-8">Privacy Policy</h1>
      <p class="text-text-light"><em>Last updated: May 2026</em></p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-8 mb-4">Information We Collect</h2>
      <p class="text-text-light leading-relaxed">
        When you make a purchase on brandblackout.com, your payment information is processed securely by Stripe. We do not store credit card numbers or sensitive payment data on our servers. Stripe may collect your name, email, shipping address, and payment details to process your order.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-8 mb-4">How We Use Your Information</h2>
      <p class="text-text-light leading-relaxed">
        We use your information solely to fulfill your orders and communicate about your purchases. We do not sell, rent, or share your personal information with third parties for marketing purposes.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-8 mb-4">Cookies</h2>
      <p class="text-text-light leading-relaxed">
        This site uses localStorage to maintain your shopping cart between page visits. No tracking cookies are used. We may use basic analytics in the future, which would be disclosed in an updated version of this policy.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-8 mb-4">Contact</h2>
      <p class="text-text-light leading-relaxed">
        For privacy-related questions, contact us at <a href="mailto:info@brandblackout.com" class="text-blackout hover:text-text-light">info@brandblackout.com</a>.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

</BaseLayout>
